textBeforeTable: CharactersEdit [show] Contents This article lists the main translations of Final Fantasy XII. These include the original Japanese version, and then their Romaji forms, and the English version. Naming changes made in the International version are indicated in brackets. If the translation for the British localization is different from that of the American localization, the change is also indicated in brackets.
